Class CrawlerDetection

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.jpl.mudrod.discoveryengine.MudrodAbstract

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class CrawlerDetection
extends LogAbstract
    An DiscoveryStepAbstract implementation which detects a known list of Web crawlers which may may be present within, and pollute various logs acting as input to Mudrod.
